PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for External Relations of Herb Davis, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a director of the Board of Directors of the International Centre for Ocean Development, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of three years, in the place of Roy Cheeseman, whose term has expired.
